</div></div>
</div></div>

</div></div>

<div class="kb-row-layout-wrap kb-row-layout-id28535_1048df-46 alignnone ambassador-block-lt wp-block-kadence-rowlayout"><div class="kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-1-columns kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-inherit kt-mobile-layout-row kt-row-valign-top">

<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column28535_11a70c-8c"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col">
<div class="wp-block-group has-background" style="background-color:#f0f0f0f0"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<div class="wp-block-group has-background" style="background-color:#f0f4f4"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
<p><strong>Step six:</strong> <strong>Crunchy Topping, Yes Please</strong></p>



<p>While your pasta is soaking up that dreamy sauce, let’s make the crispy crumb. Grab the rest of your <a class="wpil_keyword_link" href="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/parmesan-roast-cauliflower/" title="Parmesan Roast Cauliflower" data-wpil-keyword-link="linked" data-wpil-monitor-id="67" data-wpel-link="internal">roasted cauliflower</a> and give it a rough chop. Mix it with panko breadcrumbs, fresh thyme, and a little more parmesan in a bowl.</p>



<p><em>You can pop it under the grill for a minute if you want it extra crunchy—but even as is, it adds the best texture contrast.</em></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Crispy roasted cauliflower, panko bread crumbs, thyme and parmesan cheese in a glass bowl on benchtop." class="wp-image-28597" data-lazy-srcset="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9.jpg 1200w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-300x300.jpg 300w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-150x150.jpg 150w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-768x768.jpg 768w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-600x600.jpg 600w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-500x500.jpg 500w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-720x720.jpg 720w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-360x360.jpg 360w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-180x180.jpg 180w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-96x96.jpg 96w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9.jpg" alt="Crispy roasted cauliflower, panko bread crumbs, thyme and parmesan cheese in a glass bowl on benchtop." class="wp-image-28597" srcset="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9.jpg 1200w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-300x300.jpg 300w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-150x150.jpg 150w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-768x768.jpg 768w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-600x600.jpg 600w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-500x500.jpg 500w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-720x720.jpg 720w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-360x360.jpg 360w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-180x180.jpg 180w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-9-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Crispy roasted cauliflower, panko bread crumbs, thyme and parmesan cheese combined together in a glass bowl on benchtop." class="wp-image-28598" data-lazy-srcset="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10.jpg 1200w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-300x300.jpg 300w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-150x150.jpg 150w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-768x768.jpg 768w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-600x600.jpg 600w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-500x500.jpg 500w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-720x720.jpg 720w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-360x360.jpg 360w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-180x180.jpg 180w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-96x96.jpg 96w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10.jpg" alt="Crispy roasted cauliflower, panko bread crumbs, thyme and parmesan cheese combined together in a glass bowl on benchtop." class="wp-image-28598" srcset="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10.jpg 1200w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-300x300.jpg 300w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-150x150.jpg 150w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-768x768.jpg 768w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-600x600.jpg 600w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-500x500.jpg 500w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-720x720.jpg 720w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-360x360.jpg 360w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-180x180.jpg 180w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-10-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>



<p>Enjoy!</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Cauliflower alfredo sauce mixed through cooked pasta topped with crispy roasted cauliflower, panko bread crumbs, thyme, parsley and parmesan cheese in a ceramic dutch oven pan on benchtop with green and white checkered tea towel." class="wp-image-28602" data-lazy-srcset="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14.jpg 1200w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-300x300.jpg 300w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-150x150.jpg 150w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-768x768.jpg 768w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-600x600.jpg 600w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-500x500.jpg 500w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-720x720.jpg 720w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-360x360.jpg 360w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-180x180.jpg 180w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-96x96.jpg 96w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14.jpg" alt="Cauliflower alfredo sauce mixed through cooked pasta topped with crispy roasted cauliflower, panko bread crumbs, thyme, parsley and parmesan cheese in a ceramic dutch oven pan on benchtop with green and white checkered tea towel." class="wp-image-28602" srcset="https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14.jpg 1200w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-300x300.jpg 300w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-150x150.jpg 150w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-768x768.jpg 768w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-600x600.jpg 600w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-500x500.jpg 500w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-720x720.jpg 720w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-360x360.jpg 360w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-180x180.jpg 180w, https://mykidslickthebowl.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/cauliflower-alfredo-sauce-14-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>
