		<meta itemprop="description" content="This Cauliflower Alfredo Sauce is healthy, creamy, and packed with flavour! Roasted garlic, parmesan, and cauliflower blend into a smooth, velvety sauce the whole family will love. Whether you&#039;re tossing it through pasta, layering it into mac and cheese, or using it as a base for a vegetable-loaded lasagna, this creamy cauliflower sauce is a delicious way to add extra veggies to any meal. Try this Cauliflower Alfredo Sauce Healthy option for an easy dinner upgrade." />
